title: Nanosaur 2 v1.1.2
description:
THE STUNNINGLY GORGEOUS IPHONE HIT NOW AVAILABLE FOR ANDROID DEVICES!!

You're a heavily-armed flying dinosaur on a mission to save your species from extinction! How awesome is that?? Destroy everything that gets in your way as you do battle with enemy Nanosaurs and rescue stolen eggs.

++ Brilliant graphics and riveting action
++ 3 complex levels
++ Smooth, responsive tilt-control movement
++ 9 different power-ups
++ Variety of awesome weapons

What's New:

- Fixed crash on some of the new devices in the market.
